T1  - Eastern Europe's experience with banking reform: Is there a role for banks in the transition?
AU  - Thorne, Alfredo
JO  - Journal of Banking & Finance
VL  - 17
IS  - 5
SP  - 959
EP  - 1000
PY  - 1993
DA  - 1993/09/01/
